+ ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~Welcome~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

------

[[tabview]]
[[tab What is this weird land about?]]


Hey, I'm John Hammerton, or call me by my discord. You found my art page. All I'm doing here is Posting MTF insignias. I make Insignias for fun, not for a job or anything. Feel free to use them if you want. Just make sure you say I made it. 

If you want to contact me, I'm usually open on discord, my username is thedoctor7902. If you have questions or want help with anything, just DM me.

//**PLEASE NOTE, IM NEW TO THIS STUFF SO DONT SHOOT ME FOR SCREWING UP**//

[[collapsible show="Stuff that can be found" hide="You Found Some Stuff"]]
This serves for explaining each tab.

**Mainline**: I put Insignias that either are used for a main/Additional MTF, //OR// Used to be.

**New**: This is where I post Insignias for MTF that don't have one. also, here if I made it for an additional MTF that need an Insignia.

**Redone**: If I rework someone's thing or if I make a new OG insignia for a MTF that has one, it goes here.

**Non-MTF**: I put insignias here that don't have a MTF to them. They are Free use. just mention my name with it.

**//CREDIT TO TEAM//**

[[*user coyo_coya]], For letting me post Ouro-1 on here.
[[*user Woedenaz]], For the Theme. 
[[*user Jerden]], For helping me understanding how the MTF insignia system works.
People who suggested stuff, Thanks.

[[/collapsible]]
